{"tid":2172183,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美團Q2：外賣平均客單價50元，佣金率11.7% 日均2450萬單","createTime":"2020-08-24T12:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T07:50:01.000Z","uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ef8c51ad19685072fca25b58bb58144271700968","tid":2172183,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2730000/2731506/Meituan_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2730000%2F2731506%2FMeituan_1024.jpg&h=038b4481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美團點評 （03690） 交出強勁季度成績，得益於主業餐飲外賣業務強勁復甦。美團上季外賣訂單量、平均價值、收入均按年錄得增長，反映美團餐飲外賣業務已從疫情陰霾走出，表現甚至優於去年同期。美團上季餐飲外賣交易金額按年增長 17%至1088億元（人民幣，下同），日均交易筆數按年增長7%至2450萬，每筆餐飲外賣業務訂單的平均價值按年增長9.4%，帶動美團上季餐飲外賣業務恢復成長，收入按年升13%至145億元。<br />\n<br />\n今年首季中國新冠肺炎疫情爆發，消費者因衛生安全憂慮減少外賣需求，商家經營受阻，以及部分騎手未能到位，均打擊美團首季餐飲外賣業務。不過，相較首季度錄得7090萬元經營虧損，美團餐飲外賣上季錄得12.53億元經營溢利。<br />\n<br />\n若以上季度22.29億筆餐飲外賣交易筆數計算，每單經營溢利已達0.56元。參考今年首季度，每單錄經營虧損0.05元。美團曾經提出目標，在2025年前達到每天1億訂單，每單1元經營利潤。<br />\n<br />\n美團表示，上季開展各種促銷活動促進餐飲外賣業務的復甦，例如推出了「618外賣節」，令餐飲外賣訂單量實現按年增長。同時，餐飲商戶也加快線上化，美團外賣上季度新上線的品牌商家數量按年增長超過1.1倍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com//tmp/phpxgZVbg.png/big\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F%2Ftmp%2FphpxgZVbg.png%2Fbig&h=32b5e984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com//tmp/php4xtn5t.jpg/big\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F%2Ftmp%2Fphp4xtn5t.jpg%2Fbig&h=34ee470b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com//tmp/phpoMqtgO.jpg/big\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F%2Ftmp%2FphpoMqtgO.jpg%2Fbig&h=cb5d7f21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n粗略計算，美團二季度餐飲外賣業務交易額1088億元，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>平均客單價為50元左右</strong></span></span>，佣金率11.7%，與2019年整體持平。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港食肆應反思為何不藉此機會,學習內地發展外賣行業<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外賣仔梗有計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外賣仔有數圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外賣仔好賣得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有美團冇窮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有美團齊齊賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57216cc481e254fcb75cab73c7815ea7c817e134","tid":2172183,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:13:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ab68d6886039c601eeec1fa41ca22f233a70c5f","tid":2172183,"uid":178800,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:15:03.000Z","msg":"美團就係不科學<br />\n之前水災咁勁外賣生意仲節節上升?<br />\n我唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ef0290fadaa313a9d0ee8ce7329cf852a25330","tid":2172183,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:16:14.000Z","msg":"留名美團步瑞幸後塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29720d2319dce7cf0887d7c3158a27cbdd9ce70","tid":2172183,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ab68d6886039c601eeec1fa41ca22f233a70c5f","tid":2172183,"uid":178800,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:15:03.000Z","msg":"美團就係不科學<br />\n之前水災咁勁外賣生意仲節節上升?<br />\n我唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:18:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2026343/page/32\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2026343/page/32</a><br />\n呢條友都係唔信,E家夾到傻能左<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7067329ab820b8bee76213ef0a1313986e26a25f","tid":2172183,"uid":91914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33ef0290fadaa313a9d0ee8ce7329cf852a25330","tid":2